US: repetition is the mother of wisdom
It is comical that Barack Obama, the president with the reputation of more intelligent man, as a diligent student repeats in the Afghan question the strategy of his predecessor, which he took on the most stupid.
When finally revealed his Afghan approach, looking forward, demonstrated that there is a copy of the script used to Iraq by Bush, created three years ago.
Not only in the same text used several times the phrase " as in Iraq ", but do not hesitate to use the title of Bush's statement of January 2007 for his own statement: " a new way forward ".
Three years ago was himself, who criticized Bush's idea to send new military reinforcements to Iraq, the country that is suffering from the civil war and that criticized it as " an irresponsible decision and with catastrophic consequences ".
The following month, however, showed that the Bush strategy, based on the recommendations of captains of field, was the only possible and successful, so that today are not of Iraq in the news.
The reputation of Bush did not improve, however objectively left his successor an initial situation much more favourable than expected.
In Afghanistan, Barack Obama expects to repeat the miracle.
The captains of field again ask you to increase the military contingent, especially the commander - in - chief of the Afghan operation General Stanley Mccristal. He, even though the traditional relations, submitted to the rifles undecided in the White House to a harsh criticism.
Asked 40,000 men in order to improve the situation.
The president hesitated for three months, but it was nothing better, so that at least misled the general about 10,000 military.
Obtained which Europe promised another 5,000, although he previously had at least 10,000.
The most problematic of the whole strategy of Obama seems, begin to withdraw troops from Afghanistan in 18 months and finish this process in three years. The entire doctrine of Obama generated more questions than answers offered.
Many doubt that the increase give the same result that the procedure in Iraq.
In spite of the fratricidal wars in recent years, the society of Iraq is relatively well organised, its leaders respect the agreements.
The situation in Afghanistan is different: it is not possible to rely on anyone and no agreement was not satisfied.
Under these conditions, it is difficult to train the Afghan security forces, if they are used to change the head every day according to their needs.
The political institutions, although formally established, will remain only a Potemkin village. After he will remain patriarchal tribal relations.
Balancing the interests of different ethnic groups is extremely difficult due to the confusing, even more complicated by the Pakistani and Iranian influence.
Even establish a state that is capable of action, " a minimum target for the entire operation, seems very real.
The horizon of Obama's strategy comes by his voluntarism.
Over the past eight years, the situation in Afghanistan has continued to deteriorate and is now about to burst.
Only a romantic soul, who know nothing of the reality, can believe that the military sent to war to soon return home, " will do some miracle here.
From a political point of view, to set the date of the withdrawal of troops is sheer irresponsibility, since the Taliban will consider this indirectly as a statement of the American defeat.
The last NATO summit showed that the Europeans have less and less willing to participate in military operations in Afghanistan.
European politicians do not know, and do not want to explain to their constituents, what relationship has the security of Germany or Italy with the war with the Hindu Kush.
The other factor, capable of radically affect the situation, is the development of events in Iran.
If the situation continues to deteriorate and the sanctions have no effect on the Iranians, the US will have to take a difficult decision: to try to solve the problem with military force or not.
It will be necessary to find the answers precisely when, according to Obama, America starts the withdrawal of troops from Afghanistan.
However, every solution will mean a dramatic setback for the Afghan situation.
The only positive point for Barack Obama is the fact that there are three years for the presidential election and that is why there is still plenty of time to find another strategy, if this is a total failure.
The managers of the bank Goldman Sachs will not receive the cash bonuses
Senior executives of the US bank Goldman Sachs will not receive this year bonuses in cash.
The entity announced to react to the harsh criticism of its pay practices.
The group of 30 senior managers will receive, instead of money, actions that will not be sold at a minimum period of five years.
Moreover, the actions may be withdrawn in the event that they had assumed excessive risks.
According to Reuters, Goldman Sachs thus became the leader in the effort to unite the bonuses on Wall Street with the power in the long term.
I suppose that Wall Street is fully aware of the longest journey that must, mentioned the former bank investor of the entity Douglas Elliott.
The devil is in the details, he added.
The bank Goldman Sachs faced criticism after having almost $17 billion (almost 300 million CZK) for the bonuses, in the first three quarters of this year.
The total amount of bonuses in the entity for this year, according to the Reuters news agency, probably exceeds, despite the measures announced today, the $20 billion.
The high bonuses in the banking sector became, with the arrival of the financial crisis, in a sensitive issue in politics.
Great Britain announced Wednesday that it plans to tax at once, with a tax of 50 per cent, the bonuses for that exceed the 25,000 pounds (approximately 712,000 CZK) .
France is also preparing similar measures.
This year the women received the Nobel Prizes in all categories less physical
Five women, which is a record, received today in Stockholm in the hands of King Charles XVI of Sweden this year's Nobel prizes in categories, specialized and literature.
In addition to the four scientific, was among the recipients also a German writer Herta Müller of Romanian origin.
The Nobel Prize for medicine received two biologists, Elizabeth Blackburn and Carol Greider, as well as his compatriot Jack Szostak for research in the field of chromosomes.
The Nobel Prize in chemistry it received the Israeli and Americans and Thomas for the explanation of the structure and function of the ribosomas.
The final prize awarded the Nobel Prize for economics, received the American Elinor Ostrom and his compatriot Oliver Williamson for the analysis of an economic report.
The only specialist category, without a woman, was physical.
This prize received today scientists Charles Kao for research in the field of optical cables, Willard Boyle and George Smith with the invention of the chip, which constitutes the basis of all digital cameras, faxes or telescopes.
Each winner received the diploma, the Nobel medal and certificate of the money received.
This amount in each category is up to 10 billion kronor (approximately 25 million Czech crowns) .
In the case of multiple recipients in each category, the prize is shared among themselves.
The traditionally more expected Nobel, the peace, received this afternoon in Oslo, Norway, the US President Barack Obama.
In his speech acknowledged the controversy have been rewarded, as he is at the beginning of his career and is at the head of a country engaged in two wars, in Iraq and in Afghanistan.
To defend its policy added, however, that in certain situations the wars are essential to achieve peace, although its price is high.
