According to the new schedule of Čd trains move less trains for almost the same charges
České dráhy (Czech Railways) from 13 December cancelled or restringuirán some local fast trains and less used and, on the contrary, strengthen some links.
The total length of the traffic will be reduced by two per cent compared with today, after the new timetable of trains enters into force.
The majority of charges including the basic price and customer will not change.
More possibilities of links to the capital gain for example the inhabitants of the region of Ostravsko, dráhy for this line added unacarretería pendolino.
The direct train, on the contrary, will not move to Bratislava.
In the Prague - Pisek - České Budějovice move less fast trains, restringuirán direct links Prague - Letohrad.
In the regions, the largest reduction of transport planned by dráhy is in the region of, eight per cent in total, on the contrary, the transport will increase in Prague and the surrounding area.
It also cancelled two night trains in the Prague - Tábor - České Budějovice and some fast trains in line Prague - Pisek - České Budějovice will be reduced to only a few days of the week.
One of the biggest changes is the introduction of a new line of Milovice to Prague, the inhabitants of Milovice must change in Lysá nad Labem.
This is the 15. system Esko, on the outskirts of cities, its opening is possible thanks to the electrification of the line of Lysá nad Labem to Milovice.
The links to long distances to the capital will end in Prague station Hlavní nádraží.
Čd will introduce more links between Prague and Ostrava and trains Šumperk/Jeseník move every two hours.
As of 13 December travellers will not travel to Bratislava in Pendolino.
The account by the regional rail this year: 200 million more than before
The fast trains are charged and paid by the Ministry of Transport, to cover the so - called losses demonstrable Dráhy will receive next year four billion kroner in total, like this year. local trains are responsible for the regions, next year will pay eight billion kroner in total, and the state will help them almost three billion.
This year the regional trains are 200 million more expensive.
For the fast trains and local dráhy have a new contract for ten years, until now the contract was always a year.
Dráhy are happy with the system, and perhaps that is why did not increase the price of a large majority of the tickets.
The changes will occur only in tickets a day - Čd net and cheap tickets of Internet eliška.
For travellers without customer card the price Čd net increase of 450 SEK 600 SEK.
The price of eliška depend on the distance, until now the single price of 160 kroner to travel between any two regional cities.
Filipino armed continue arresting more than 50 people, the children were released
The gunmen have kidnapped in the southern Philippines 75 people, including several pupils of a primary school and their teachers.
So said the AFP agency, which previously reported only about 65 abducted.
All 17 children and a teacher were released after eight hours.
The kidnapping occurred in the Agusan del Sur province.
They say that approximately 19 armed used hostages as a shield live in the brain to the police.
The local negotiators are trying to agree on the delivery of the remaining hostages.
According to the AFP agency armed belong to the new People's Army (NPA) , a fraction of the Communist Party of the Philippines (CPP) .
According to the PA police agency previously pursued the kidnappers due to the violence, whose cause was the ajustamiento accounts between two clans of the local families.
In the southern Philippines in Maguindanao province was because of the recent massacre, in which 57 people died, imposed martial law.
Among the victims of the massacre of 23. November, related to the election of the governor, were 30 journalists.
For the suspicion of involvement in the killing arrested the governor of the province in the southern Philippines and his father Andal Ampatuan, patriarch of a dynasty of the Ampatuan.
On the island of Mindanao operate also Muslim separatists.
However them on Tuesday renewed peace talks with the Philippine government.
The history of RSA relates to the whole world, says Morgan Freeman alias Mandela
In the coming days will close in US cinemas a new Hollywood movie, Clint Eastwood Invictus (his official title in Czech esinvictus: Neporažený) , which captures a part of the biography of the former President of the Republic of South Africa Nelson Mandela.
The role of the globally known fighter against apartheid is Morgan Freeman, who chose years ago for the leading role the Mandela.
The second part, the legendary champion in rugby, interpreted Matt Damon.
With the premiere born of the reactions of the critics and the public
Nelson Mandela
His full name is Nelson Mandela. Was born the 18. July 1918 in Mvezo, South Africa.
In 1988 received the Sakharov Prize for freedom of thought, in 1993 received, together with the de Klerk, the Nobel Peace Prize.
Was President of the Republic of South Africa in the years 1994-1999.
High hopes, to the public at the time, when in the Republic of South Africa complete preparations for the World Cup in football. At the same time the media are by alarming news about the growing racial hatred and discrimination of the inhabitants of the dominant black majority.
According to the news agency, the reactions to this new film in RSA have been positive, despite numerous reservations against the distribution of roles for the " interesting " Hollywood stars.
Morgan Freeman however says, that is proud of the film.
For many years dreamed of the role and I was prepared to play.
Many times I met in person with Nelson Mandela, for - as they say - charge their energy, said in an interview after the festive debut in Los Angeles.
I think it is good, whether through the film we can remember the character and the message of Mandela.
It is a history of the Republic of South Africa, perose refers to the whole world, he added.
In the dress of the national rugby team
The film is based on the book of the British writer John Carlin with the title freely translated into the role of the enemy: Nelson Mandela and the game. Thanks to this game was born the nation. Portrays the South African human rights lawyer during his first presidential election.
Morgan Freeman in the film is trying to unite two groups of people, and for long years separated. Like Nelson Mandela in 1995, he was also puts the national dress of the South African team of rugby and RSA won at the time the World Cup.
By entering the gramilla in the clothes, that RSA is seen as something almost sacred, Mandela fourteen years ago won large, especially of the public white and the recognition of the white people.
The football championship will perhaps help people to unite and form a nation, mentioned the rugby player Chester Williams, the only " black " in the national team in 1995.
Still will be if it improves the tense situation in the RSA.
White South Africans are however sceptical, as for example in an interview for LN an amateur rugby Christopher Dawson, who fled their country to Britain.
The championship starts on 11 June 2010.
