The case Kunduz
Frontal attack the opposition: the head of the Group of the Greens, Jürgen Trittin, called liar the Minister of Defence, Gutenberg, due to false information on the subject.
The SPD and the leftist require explanation to the Chancellor.
Hamburg/Berlin - following the most recent revelations about the air strike in Kunduz, the opposition has criticized the Minister of Defence, Karl - Theodor zu Gutenberg (CSU) , with knowledge of the facts.
In the transmission of news " Tagesschau " on Saturday, transmitted by the television channel ARD, the head of the Group of the Greens, Jürgen Trittin, said that the minister had not told the truth " about the deadly bombing of two convoys.
In such a case, usually says: he told lies.
The order to kill would have been given without taking into account the rules of the international force protection for Afghanistan (ISAF) .
This is the essence of the report that had NATO, and read the Gutenberg, said Trittin.
