The Brazilian Government has put to the permanence of Manuel Zelaya in its embassy in Tegucigalpa.
The deposed president must abandon the embassy diplomatic 27 January 2010 at the latest, when officially completed its mandate.
Francisco Catunda, chargé d'affaires of Brazil's embassy in the Honduran capital, confirmed to TV globe that " Mel " knows that he must leave before that date of the embassy, where refugee from 21 September.
" He is aware that must come on 27 January, at the end of his term, it has to seek another destination ".
The station also quoted the former agent, who confirmed his intention to leave the embassy before the deadline: " My position is leaving as soon as possible, naturally with the support of the government of Brazil, " declared Zelaya telephone.
After the elections on 29 November (in which was elected Porfirio Lobo) , Zelaya assured that remain in the Brazilian embassy until January.
However, this week tried to seek refuge in Brazil.
The operation was finally frustrated by rejecting Zelaya the status of political refugee who sought to impose the government " de facto President Roberto Micheletti.
Thank you
After days of wine and roses since last spring in which the inflation of assets has been the dominant pattern in the markets, new uncertainty returned to reappear in the markets, which must not be surprising since it is their natural state, in an environment in which the actors take decisions on the future nature uncertain.
The medicine used by central banks to stabilize markets was monetize debt with direct purchase of assets and indirectly giving free rein for liquidity at rates close to zero for the financial institutions purchasing assets to discount.
The central banks have already confirmed that the direct purchases of assets have virtually completed and, without questioning their heterodox policy of liquidity, to throw some sand in the wheels how did the ECB with its auction to the year of the next week.
Therefore, the investors doubt the ability of the global economy to maintain economic recovery without measures as heterodox and we are seeing a reversal of the reduction of risk premiums.
The volatility of the stock markets and the spreads on corporate bonds have returned to rally, although still far from the levels paranormales that reached at the beginning of the year.
The States were forced to nationalise private risk and public debt returned to be affected.
Again there is a flight to quality and the US, Japan and Germany have been the refuge chosen by investors, causing an extension of the differences of the euro - zone countries with regard to Germany.
Spain had been affected by this episode of instability but in that Standard& Poor's and threatened with a new downward revision of the characterization of the Kingdom of Spain.
On the other hand, some uncertainty is not wrong to silence the defenders of the moral hazard that tried again to create awareness on those responsible for the global economic policy for the destructive effects of the restriction on the destruction of employment, when what we should do is to order a new day of Thanksgiving.
However, Dubai it portrays a tribal struggle between the emirs to reshape the power in the Emirates and Greece we have seen before.
A government that conceals public deficit, elections and a new government that is pulling the blanket.
Prodi in Italy after Berlusconi and Socrates in Portugal after Durão Barroso.
It makes no sense that the Ecofin salvase Hungary of a breach of its external payments at the beginning of the year and that will allow a member country of the euro to meet its commitments.
What makes sense is that Ecofin has forced the Greek Government to be transparent and responsible to its citizens of the need for extraordinary measures to maintain the stability of public finances.
If, how we hope, we are faced with an episode of normalization of risk premiums, after some excesses in leveraged positions, would be within expectations.
In the case of Spain, while our public debt spreads extended like the European corporate bonds should not worry.
If European differentials falling and our continued to expand, then it would be risk Spanish.
The Standard& Poor's is an anecdote. When our indicators are forcing the majority of services of studies to anticipate their scenarios of recovery and to revise upward its scenario for 2011, including the OECD and the European Commission, to return to the fray with a Japanese scenario for the Spanish economy does not life expectancy to its warning.
Again, it is the whole pint will be an excellent opportunity to buy assets Spanish, although for the moment " prudence, friend driver ".
