Play the champions has brought 476,4 million to Madrid and Barca since its origin
The Champions League has become a source of income for clubs since she was born in 1992.
Therefore, Real Madrid and Barcelona have entered 476,4 million since then, that makes them the third and fifth club that more money have won in the competition.
The leader of the list is Manchester United.
The leader of the list is Manchester United.
Winning the UEFA Champions League not only provides glory. It is also one of the main sources of income of the big clubs.
So much so that the competition has distributed 5.362,5 million euros to the 105 teams (12 of them Spanish) who have participated in the event since the tournament was created in the season 1992/1993, according to data from UEFA.
The Real Madrid and F. C. Barcelona have come out well from this distribution.
The white club has been the third of the continent that more money has been pocketed by participating, and the only, along with AC Milan, which has won the trophy three times.
The Catalan, the current champion and the last winner of the European Cup in 1992, is the fifth of the classification.
The list of the leading Manchester United and Bayern Munich, the two teams, moreover, more money billed to participate the last Champions League.
And that, despite losing both against Barca.
On the other hand, Spain is only the third country that more money has achieved through the champions, despite having achieved more titles than any other (five, four of Italy, the three of England and Germany) .
Distribution
This apparent paradox is explained by the complicated procedure of distribution of money that applied by UEFA.
For this exercise, the body chaired by Michel Platini expected join 1.09 billion for the Champions League.
Of This money UEFA will 413,1 million for fixed payments: each of the 20 clubs who participated in the previous round of classification (including Atlético Madrid) received 2.1 million.
Moreover, those who managed to participate received 3.8 million just by being there, in addition to other euros for each party.
There is also bonus for winning (800,000 euros) and empatar (400,000 for each team) . The octavofinalistas will receive three million each; the eight cuartofinalistas, 3.3 million.
The last four embolsarán 4 million each.
